FBIS4-35118 "drlat125_r_94007" FBIS-LAT-94-125 Daily Report 23 Jun 1994 Peru New Army Chief of Staff Installed New Army Chief of Staff Installed PY2806204794 Lima EXPRESO in Spanish 23 Jun 94 p A2 PY2806204794 Lima EXPRESO Spanish BFN [Excerpt] Peruvian Army Commander Nicolas Hermoza Rios yesterday installed Peruvian Army Division General Maximo Efrain Bracamonte Vargas as the new chief of staff. The ceremony was held at the Marshal Caceres Hall of the Army garrison. Bracamonte Vargas was previously the inspector general of the Army. [passage omitted]
